dataset.description:
Primary Zoning for Cuyahoga County, Ohio.
It consists of zoning areas as recorded and maintained by the Cuyahoga County Fiscal Officer.
  • Zoning By Type: areas grouped and symbolized by zoning type
This dataset is meant to take local municipal zoning regulations (MUNI_ZONE_CODE field) and normalize them across the County (ZONE_USE code). This allows the Fiscal Office to compare zoning areas from different municipalities.
Please contact the local community zoning officials for any questions regarding local zoning information.
dataset.title: Zoning for Cuyahoga County

dataset.description: Tax Parcels with CAMA Real Property characteristics within Cuyahoga County. Point parcels have been converted to polygons and combined with air parcels and survey parcels for a single parcel featureclass. This layer contains only parcels NOT in Cleveland. This data represents a shapshot in time of parcel geometries and various CAMA Real Property characteristics from multiple sources. Last updated JUNE 2019. FOR USE IN THE OPEN DATA APPLICATION.
dataset.title: Combined Parcels - Non-Cleveland Only
